                        <join result="offenceCrimeDate" targOrder="Y" targets="t18450707-1552-offence-1 t18450707-cd-31"></join>28th of June</rs>, 4 half-crowns, 13 shillings, 1 sixpence, 7 pence, and 2 farthings, the monies of <persName id="t18450707-name-522" type="victimName">
